WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:08.240
Hi, I'm Iva Kraljevic

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:08.800
and welcome to

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:09.380
the podcast.

00:00:09.779 --> 00:00:10.160
Today I have the honor

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:11.179
to speak with

00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:14.013
an exceptional guest

00:00:14.179 --> 00:00:15.000
her name is

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.260
Ramona Trevino,

00:00:16.820 --> 00:00:17.559
if I pronounce

00:00:17.559 --> 00:00:18.239
it correctly.

00:00:18.679 --> 00:00:19.260
Yes, that is

00:00:19.260 --> 00:00:20.059
correct, good job.

00:00:20.579 --> 00:00:22.440
Ramona is a person whose

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:24.379
life story resonated strongly

00:00:24.379 --> 00:00:25.719
in the pro-life community,

00:00:25.719 --> 00:00:26.699
and today we

00:00:26.699 --> 00:00:27.480
will hear why.

00:00:28.019 --> 00:00:30.480
And how she went

00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:31.940
from leading a

00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:33.420
Planned Parenthood clinic

00:00:34.531 --> 00:00:35.115
to becoming a passionate

00:00:35.115 --> 00:00:36.116
advocate for the

00:00:36.116 --> 00:00:37.533
protection of life

00:00:37.533 --> 00:00:39.160
from conception,

00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:40.119
and pivotal experiences

00:00:40.119 --> 00:00:42.955
that transforemed her
along the way.

00:00:42.955 --> 00:00:45.874
(music)

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:52.380
Dear Ramona,

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:53.399
it's really an

00:00:53.399 --> 00:00:54.619
honor and a pleasure

00:00:54.619 --> 00:00:55.399
having you here.

00:00:55.679 --> 00:00:56.060
Thank you for

00:00:56.060 --> 00:00:56.560
being here.

00:00:57.079 --> 00:00:57.619
And thank you for

00:00:57.619 --> 00:00:58.960
being willing to share your

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:00.000
powerful story with

00:01:00.039 --> 00:01:01.039
our podcast listeners.

00:01:01.340 --> 00:01:02.359
Well, it's definitely my

00:01:02.359 --> 00:01:03.159
honor to be here

00:01:03.159 --> 00:01:03.960
with you in Croatia.

00:01:04.340 --> 00:01:04.840
Such a blessing,

00:01:05.159 --> 00:01:06.159
so thank you. How do

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:07.079
you like Croatia so far?

00:01:07.099 --> 00:01:07.879
I'm loving it,

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:08.400
it's beautiful.

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:09.700
I hope we will see

00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:10.519
you again here.

00:01:10.540 --> 00:01:11.719
I hope so, yes. Okay,

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:14.260
let's start,

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:14.780
shall we?

00:01:15.459 --> 00:01:15.780
Maybe from

00:01:15.780 --> 00:01:16.280
the beginning.

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:18.099
How did you end

00:01:18.099 --> 00:01:19.299
up working for the

00:01:19.319 --> 00:01:20.700
Planned Parenthood in

00:01:20.700 --> 00:01:21.280
the first place?

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:23.000
And what made you

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:24.959
reconsider your role there?

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:26.920
Yes,
so as you can

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:28.400
imagine that is the

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:30.459
most popular question

00:01:30.459 --> 00:01:31.819
that people have

00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:34.680
because especially

00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:36.859
coming from Planned

00:01:36.859 --> 00:01:38.019
Parenthood and then

00:01:38.019 --> 00:01:39.540
now becoming pro-life,

00:01:39.629 --> 00:01:40.780
the first question is

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:41.799
how did you end

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:42.480
up at Planned Parenthood,

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:43.420
right?

00:01:43.540 --> 00:01:44.180
And I think for

00:01:44.180 --> 00:01:46.579
most former workers,

00:01:46.879 --> 00:01:47.640
abortion workers,

00:01:48.159 --> 00:01:49.200
that is probably

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.519
one of the most

00:01:50.519 --> 00:01:51.480
common questions.

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.079
And I've spent

00:01:53.079 --> 00:01:53.620
a lot of time,

00:01:54.519 --> 00:01:55.939
especially

00:01:55.939 --> 00:01:56.739
since leaving,

00:01:57.299 --> 00:01:58.000
over the years

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.040
thinking about that

00:01:59.379 --> 00:01:59.859
because I don't

00:01:59.859 --> 00:02:00.579
think it's just a

00:02:00.579 --> 00:02:01.810
very simple answer.

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:03.939
I think for many

00:02:03.939 --> 00:02:05.060
of us it's more

00:02:05.060 --> 00:02:06.760
complicated as to

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:07.640
how we end up at

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:08.840
Planned Parenthood. And I think

00:02:09.379 --> 00:02:09.879
what

00:02:10.180 --> 00:02:11.900
I've come to terms with

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:14.099
is a very easy answer,

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:17.139
which is satan capitalizes on

00:02:17.139 --> 00:02:19.080
our trauma and our sin.

00:02:19.819 --> 00:02:20.680
And he looks for an

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:22.139
opportunity to take

00:02:22.139 --> 00:02:23.080
advantage of us when

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:23.740
we're vulnerable.

00:02:24.860 --> 00:02:26.699
And obviously I played

00:02:26.699 --> 00:02:29.439
a role in accepting the

00:02:29.439 --> 00:02:30.439
position for working

00:02:30.439 --> 00:02:31.740
for Planned Parenthood.

00:02:32.159 --> 00:02:33.479
But then when I

00:02:33.479 --> 00:02:34.460
dive a little deeper

00:02:34.460 --> 00:02:35.639
into my past,

00:02:35.639 --> 00:02:38.139
I realized why I was

00:02:38.139 --> 00:02:39.300
so easily deceived

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:40.840
into believing that

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:41.759
I was helping women.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:43.539
And that I

00:02:43.539 --> 00:02:44.740
think came from,

00:02:45.719 --> 00:02:46.900
I was a teen mom,

00:02:47.300 --> 00:02:48.479
so I became pregnant

00:02:48.479 --> 00:02:49.560
at 16 years old

00:02:50.159 --> 00:02:51.000
and had my daughter

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:51.879
when I was 17.

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:53.020
But I was in

00:02:53.020 --> 00:02:54.199
a very abusive relationship

00:02:54.199 --> 00:02:54.979
with the father

00:02:54.979 --> 00:02:56.020
of my daughter

00:02:56.699 --> 00:02:57.280
for eight years

00:02:57.659 --> 00:03:00.360
and then finally found

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:01.379
the courage to

00:03:01.379 --> 00:03:03.000
leave that abusive relationship

00:03:03.599 --> 00:03:04.300
and face life as

00:03:04.300 --> 00:03:04.960
a single mother.

00:03:05.659 --> 00:03:06.740
But I never sought

00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:08.539
healing from that trauma.

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:12.360
I never sought any

00:03:12.360 --> 00:03:13.379
type of psychological

00:03:13.379 --> 00:03:15.939
help or therapy or I

00:03:15.939 --> 00:03:16.960
didn't even go to God

00:03:17.030 --> 00:03:19.319
to ask for those wounds

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:20.319
to be healed and there

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:21.360
were a lot of wounds.

00:03:22.060 --> 00:03:22.680
And so I think,

00:03:22.939 --> 00:03:24.199
when I think about it,

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:26.039
when this

00:03:26.039 --> 00:03:27.259
opportunity presented

00:03:27.259 --> 00:03:28.180
itself to work for

00:03:28.199 --> 00:03:28.879
Planned Parenthood,

00:03:29.759 --> 00:03:31.340
because abortions didn't

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:33.120
happen under my roof,

00:03:33.539 --> 00:03:34.259
they weren't happening

00:03:34.259 --> 00:03:35.180
in that center,

00:03:35.740 --> 00:03:36.699
I thought that I

00:03:36.699 --> 00:03:38.939
was helping prevent

00:03:38.939 --> 00:03:40.259
young women from

00:03:40.259 --> 00:03:41.340
experiencing the

00:03:41.340 --> 00:03:41.960
things that I had

00:03:41.960 --> 00:03:42.659
once experienced.

00:03:43.780 --> 00:03:44.520
And I never stopped

00:03:44.659 --> 00:03:46.180
to consider really what

00:03:46.180 --> 00:03:47.460
I was involved in.

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:48.699
And so I think that's

00:03:48.759 --> 00:03:49.919
probably a little

00:03:49.919 --> 00:03:50.539
bit more of a

00:03:50.539 --> 00:03:52.639
longer answer to it.

00:03:52.639 --> 00:03:53.659
But the simple answer

00:03:53.659 --> 00:03:54.599
is that's where we

00:03:54.599 --> 00:03:55.840
often see that satan

00:03:56.500 --> 00:03:57.340
has a way of

00:03:57.979 --> 00:03:59.080
taking advantage of us

00:03:59.080 --> 00:04:00.060
in our vulnerability

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:01.080
and in our wounds

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:01.599
and our hurts.

00:04:02.620 --> 00:04:03.000
And one of the

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.539
reasons why I always encourage

00:04:04.900 --> 00:04:05.979
people to seek healing,

00:04:06.780 --> 00:04:07.259
whether it be

00:04:07.259 --> 00:04:08.639
professionally from a

00:04:08.639 --> 00:04:09.960
therapist or from

00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:11.240
the greatest healer,

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:12.400
which is Jesus Christ,

00:04:12.620 --> 00:04:14.780
who is capable of

00:04:14.780 --> 00:04:15.780
healing all wounds

00:04:15.780 --> 00:04:17.920
to never leave those

00:04:17.920 --> 00:04:19.240
things unhealed

00:04:19.860 --> 00:04:20.759
because Satan will

00:04:20.759 --> 00:04:21.379
definitely find

00:04:21.439 --> 00:04:22.279
a way to capitalize

00:04:22.399 --> 00:04:23.139
on those wounds.

00:04:24.180 --> 00:04:26.040
And what was the turning

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:28.519
point before that?

00:04:28.779 --> 00:04:31.339
What did you experience at

00:04:31.379 --> 00:04:33.620
your job that made you,

00:04:34.379 --> 00:04:35.180
as I said, reconsider

00:04:35.180 --> 00:04:37.939
or just maybe you

00:04:38.079 --> 00:04:39.399
felt disappointed or

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:40.660
what was it like?

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:41.420
Yeah,

00:04:41.439 --> 00:04:42.240
so I directed this

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:42.959
clinic for three

00:04:42.959 --> 00:04:45.639
years. And I think

00:04:46.420 --> 00:04:47.500
for a while,

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:48.959
especially

00:04:48.959 --> 00:04:49.639
after leaving,

00:04:50.019 --> 00:04:50.519
I thought,

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:52.019
well, I wasn't

00:04:52.019 --> 00:04:53.079
really involved in

00:04:54.019 --> 00:04:55.420
really truly evil

00:04:55.420 --> 00:04:56.379
because we weren't

00:04:56.379 --> 00:04:57.060
doing abortions.

00:04:57.319 --> 00:04:59.040
And then God really

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.199
started to reveal to

00:05:00.199 --> 00:05:01.120
me over time that,

00:05:01.620 --> 00:05:02.779
yes, I was involved

00:05:02.779 --> 00:05:03.519
in evil things.

00:05:03.779 --> 00:05:04.519
And so if you

00:05:04.519 --> 00:05:05.680
talk to someone who

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:08.120
directly worked in abortion,

00:05:08.300 --> 00:05:10.459
who directly saw the

00:05:10.459 --> 00:05:11.779
abortions take place,

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.620
there's a different level

00:05:14.620 --> 00:05:16.740
to all of this,

00:05:16.879 --> 00:05:17.560
another layer,

00:05:17.740 --> 00:05:18.259
if you will.

00:05:19.279 --> 00:05:19.839
And for me,

00:05:20.879 --> 00:05:21.800
I spent those three

00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:23.069
years justifying,

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:24.699
oh, well, I'm not

00:05:24.699 --> 00:05:25.860
doing abortions here.

00:05:26.019 --> 00:05:26.519
It's happening

00:05:26.819 --> 00:05:27.339
somewhere else.

00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:28.579
We're just referring

00:05:28.579 --> 00:05:30.360
women for abortions.

00:05:31.100 --> 00:05:32.300
And that's what was

00:05:32.300 --> 00:05:33.500
weighing on my heart,

00:05:34.100 --> 00:05:36.019
that I was referring

00:05:36.019 --> 00:05:37.019
women for abortions,

00:05:37.220 --> 00:05:37.959
but I tried the

00:05:37.959 --> 00:05:39.839
whole time to ignore that.

00:05:40.009 --> 00:05:41.779
But what I couldn't

00:05:41.779 --> 00:05:43.079
ignore was that I was

00:05:43.079 --> 00:05:43.920
helping create a

00:05:43.920 --> 00:05:44.879
market for abortions,

00:05:45.579 --> 00:05:47.160
because really the majority

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:48.779
of the women that

00:05:48.779 --> 00:05:49.540
were coming into

00:05:49.579 --> 00:05:50.040
Planned Parenthood

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:50.540
weren't women.

00:05:51.160 --> 00:05:51.680
They were children.

00:05:52.420 --> 00:05:52.839
And so we're

00:05:52.839 --> 00:05:54.079
talking young girls,

00:05:54.519 --> 00:05:55.319
you know, 15,

00:05:55.519 --> 00:05:56.980
16, 17 years old,

00:05:57.540 --> 00:05:58.579
who are living

00:05:58.579 --> 00:05:59.399
promiscuously,

00:06:00.079 --> 00:06:01.319
who are there to get

00:06:01.319 --> 00:06:02.199
on birth control.

00:06:02.699 --> 00:06:03.480
And then ultimately

00:06:03.480 --> 00:06:04.519
when those things

00:06:04.519 --> 00:06:06.100
fail and when

00:06:06.100 --> 00:06:08.000
that lifestyle catches up

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:09.040
to them, if you will,

00:06:09.399 --> 00:06:10.759
they seek abortions.

00:06:11.319 --> 00:06:12.199
And so you're just creating

00:06:12.199 --> 00:06:15.199
this revolving door of a

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:16.959
market that ultimately

00:06:16.959 --> 00:06:18.519
leads these young

00:06:18.519 --> 00:06:19.399
girls to abortion.

00:06:19.779 --> 00:06:20.500
And that was weighing

00:06:20.500 --> 00:06:21.560
heavily on my heart,

00:06:21.579 --> 00:06:22.639
because I could see

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:24.399
that I wasn't helping

00:06:24.399 --> 00:06:26.500
prevent these young women

00:06:26.500 --> 00:06:28.120
from being in situations like

00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:29.100
I had once been in.

00:06:29.480 --> 00:06:30.100
The only thing I was

00:06:30.100 --> 00:06:31.199
preventing was children,

00:06:31.420 --> 00:06:34.500
right?
But the abuse and the

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:36.160
objectification that

00:06:36.240 --> 00:06:37.120
they were subjecting

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:38.779
themselves to was there,

00:06:39.180 --> 00:06:39.579
you know?

00:06:39.579 --> 00:06:40.399
And so I was helping

00:06:40.399 --> 00:06:42.879
perpetuate that in these

00:06:42.939 --> 00:06:43.560
young girls' lives.

00:06:43.579 --> 00:06:44.660
So you did refer them.

00:06:45.100 --> 00:06:47.639
You,
can I say, sent

00:06:47.639 --> 00:06:49.759
them to the other facility?

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:50.620
Yes.

00:06:50.959 --> 00:06:51.819
To do the abortion?

00:06:51.939 --> 00:06:52.560
Yeah, because we

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:53.199
were all part of

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:54.240
the same affiliate.

00:06:54.470 --> 00:06:57.120
And so I think there

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:58.759
were maybe 26 or 27,

00:06:58.759 --> 00:06:59.339
I don't remember

00:06:59.339 --> 00:07:00.040
the exact number,

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:02.720
clinics in that Planned

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:03.579
Parenthood affiliate.

00:07:04.279 --> 00:07:06.560
Two of those are where

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.100
the women went to

00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:08.860
get their abortions.

00:07:09.519 --> 00:07:10.399
And so everywhere

00:07:10.399 --> 00:07:11.899
else were the family

00:07:11.899 --> 00:07:12.839
planning centers,

00:07:12.839 --> 00:07:13.800
but still part of

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:14.740
the same affiliate.

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:15.920
And so we were

00:07:15.920 --> 00:07:17.839
sending everyone into those two,

00:07:18.220 --> 00:07:18.720
you know,

00:07:19.180 --> 00:07:20.000
either one of those two

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:20.899
abortion facilities.

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:22.279
And so at the

00:07:22.279 --> 00:07:23.000
end of the day,

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.220
when I received

00:07:24.220 --> 00:07:24.860
my paycheck,

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:25.860
you know,

00:07:26.019 --> 00:07:26.379
with Planned

00:07:26.379 --> 00:07:27.199
Parenthood on it,

00:07:27.579 --> 00:07:28.160
it was still

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:28.660
blood money,

00:07:29.339 --> 00:07:30.300
you know, because it was

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:31.860
all going into one pot,

00:07:32.399 --> 00:07:33.620
one money pot.

00:07:34.360 --> 00:07:34.899
And I was still

00:07:34.899 --> 00:07:35.939
getting paid with blood money.

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:37.060
And I tried to

00:07:37.060 --> 00:07:37.620
ignore that,

00:07:37.939 --> 00:07:38.860
you know, I didn't

00:07:38.860 --> 00:07:39.600
want to think about it.

00:07:40.060 --> 00:07:41.079
I still wanted to

00:07:41.079 --> 00:07:42.300
convince myself,

00:07:42.300 --> 00:07:43.420
you know, that I was

00:07:43.420 --> 00:07:44.300
doing good things,

00:07:44.300 --> 00:07:45.600
that I wasn't any

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:46.899
different than working for

00:07:46.899 --> 00:07:48.300
a gynecologist or any

00:07:48.300 --> 00:07:49.339
other physician. Right.

00:07:49.860 --> 00:07:50.759
But I realized, no,

00:07:51.259 --> 00:07:52.240
it's not the same

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:53.000
thing at all.

00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:54.060
It's an exploitation

00:07:54.060 --> 00:07:55.800
of women and especially

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:57.279
young girls and

00:07:57.279 --> 00:07:58.879
getting them really to

00:07:59.139 --> 00:08:01.139
forget about any type

00:08:01.180 --> 00:08:02.120
of sense of morality

00:08:03.019 --> 00:08:03.819
when it comes to

00:08:03.819 --> 00:08:05.740
their sexuality and

00:08:05.740 --> 00:08:07.139
removing any type

00:08:07.139 --> 00:08:08.759
of stigma, you know,

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.420
surrounding promiscuity

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:12.920
