And then they were

00:24:17.750 --> 00:24:19.009
just there in every

00:24:19.009 --> 00:24:19.809
way that they could

00:24:19.809 --> 00:24:21.990
be in the beginning

00:24:21.990 --> 00:24:23.349
while we transitioned

00:24:23.349 --> 00:24:25.250
to not having

00:24:25.799 --> 00:24:26.789
that income. But

00:24:26.789 --> 00:24:28.089
yeah, they were

00:24:28.089 --> 00:24:28.789
always supportive.

00:24:29.049 --> 00:24:30.210
And I believe that

00:24:30.210 --> 00:24:31.849
I'm here today right

00:24:31.849 --> 00:24:34.390
now in Croatia because

00:24:34.390 --> 00:24:35.549
of all the prayers of

00:24:35.549 --> 00:24:37.710
the faithful who pray

00:24:37.710 --> 00:24:38.630
for my protection,

00:24:38.869 --> 00:24:40.009
who pray for my safety,

00:24:40.680 --> 00:24:43.150
pray for my travels and

00:24:43.150 --> 00:24:44.450
just pray for the work

00:24:44.450 --> 00:24:45.529
that I continue to do.

00:24:45.730 --> 00:24:46.430
I couldn't do it

00:24:46.430 --> 00:24:47.690
without the prayers.

00:24:47.720 --> 00:24:48.890
You've shared that the

00:24:48.890 --> 00:24:50.269
major turning point was

00:24:50.269 --> 00:24:52.269
listening to this Catholic

00:24:52.420 --> 00:24:53.769
radio while driving.

00:24:55.700 --> 00:24:56.289
What's your opinion?

00:24:56.940 --> 00:24:58.230
How the media can

00:24:58.230 --> 00:25:04.349
be powerful or is it

00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:06.089
important to share on

00:25:06.089 --> 00:25:08.559
the podcasts or anywhere?

00:25:09.109 --> 00:25:09.690
Or even through

00:25:09.690 --> 00:25:10.690
social media, yeah.

00:25:11.369 --> 00:25:12.609
All the outlets, I

00:25:12.609 --> 00:25:14.789
think it's very critical

00:25:14.789 --> 00:25:15.710
for us to be able

00:25:15.710 --> 00:25:17.230
to do this and important.

00:25:18.680 --> 00:25:19.410
And I think one of

00:25:19.410 --> 00:25:21.009
the main reasons is

00:25:21.009 --> 00:25:22.990
because obviously, one,

00:25:23.299 --> 00:25:23.809
you're reaching

00:25:23.809 --> 00:25:24.910
more people than you

00:25:24.980 --> 00:25:25.569
would otherwise.

00:25:26.269 --> 00:25:27.150
But also because

00:25:27.150 --> 00:25:28.509
sometimes when people

00:25:28.509 --> 00:25:30.269
are struggling,

00:25:30.960 --> 00:25:31.769
whether it be with

00:25:31.769 --> 00:25:32.609
their faith or

00:25:32.609 --> 00:25:33.609
whether it's on this

00:25:33.609 --> 00:25:34.369
issue of abortion,

00:25:34.490 --> 00:25:35.269
whatever it is, right?

00:25:35.940 --> 00:25:36.440
When people

00:25:36.440 --> 00:25:37.049
are struggling,

00:25:38.099 --> 00:25:40.049
I think it's helpful

00:25:40.049 --> 00:25:41.710
for them to be

00:25:41.710 --> 00:25:43.349
able to process these

00:25:43.349 --> 00:25:44.279
things in private.

00:25:45.259 --> 00:25:45.759
For me,

00:25:46.059 --> 00:25:47.289
it wasn't a topic I

00:25:47.289 --> 00:25:48.369
was willing to discuss

00:25:48.369 --> 00:25:49.170
with other people.

00:25:49.769 --> 00:25:50.589
I didn't talk about

00:25:50.589 --> 00:25:51.190
it with friends.

00:25:51.450 --> 00:25:52.109
I didn't talk about

00:25:52.109 --> 00:25:52.970
it with my husband.

00:25:53.589 --> 00:25:54.349
I didn't talk about

00:25:54.349 --> 00:25:55.329
it with my family.

00:25:55.869 --> 00:25:56.470
When I was going

00:25:56.470 --> 00:25:57.269
through this process,

00:25:57.390 --> 00:25:58.309
I was going through

00:25:58.309 --> 00:25:59.910
it alone in the beginning.

00:26:00.779 --> 00:26:01.750
And I think it

00:26:01.750 --> 00:26:04.549
was helpful to have Catholic

00:26:04.549 --> 00:26:06.230
radio, that media there,

00:26:06.740 --> 00:26:07.240
to help

00:26:08.740 --> 00:26:10.150
walk me through the process

00:26:10.150 --> 00:26:12.109
but privately in my car.

00:26:12.950 --> 00:26:14.750
I didn't have to

00:26:14.750 --> 00:26:15.750
get in any discussions

00:26:15.750 --> 00:26:17.170
with people over it.

00:26:17.349 --> 00:26:17.890
It was just

00:26:17.890 --> 00:26:19.349
straightforward to me,

00:26:19.759 --> 00:26:20.549
to my heart. And

00:26:20.549 --> 00:26:21.250
it always felt

00:26:21.250 --> 00:26:22.390
as if God was

00:26:22.390 --> 00:26:23.809
speaking directly to me

00:26:23.809 --> 00:26:25.710
through whoever it was that

00:26:25.710 --> 00:26:26.650
was on the radio

00:26:26.650 --> 00:26:28.630
and whatever program they had.

00:26:28.630 --> 00:26:29.549
And so I think

00:26:29.549 --> 00:26:32.430
it's very important that we

00:26:32.430 --> 00:26:34.089
have the courage to

00:26:34.089 --> 00:26:34.950
talk about these topics,

00:26:35.430 --> 00:26:36.269
especially on

00:26:36.680 --> 00:26:38.109
media outlets.

00:26:39.410 --> 00:26:39.869
And what would be

00:26:39.869 --> 00:26:40.670
your message to

00:26:40.670 --> 00:26:41.910
somebody who maybe

00:26:41.910 --> 00:26:45.769
already feels convicted

00:26:45.880 --> 00:26:47.480
or at least conflicted?

00:26:50.720 --> 00:26:51.640
What would be

00:26:51.640 --> 00:26:52.319
your message?

00:26:53.740 --> 00:26:55.039
Are you referring to

00:26:55.039 --> 00:26:56.440
someone who's working in

00:26:56.440 --> 00:26:57.480
the abortion industry?

00:26:59.319 --> 00:27:01.000
Yeah, maybe somebody who

00:27:01.000 --> 00:27:03.380
needs to quit their job.

00:27:03.839 --> 00:27:04.440
It's not an

00:27:04.440 --> 00:27:05.599
easy decision.

00:27:06.319 --> 00:27:09.299
No. I think it's

00:27:09.299 --> 00:27:10.599
difficult and I always want

00:27:10.599 --> 00:27:11.619
to be mindful that

00:27:11.619 --> 00:27:13.359
we're not all the same.

00:27:14.099 --> 00:27:16.299
I think for me,

00:27:18.559 --> 00:27:19.859
I have a certain type

00:27:19.859 --> 00:27:22.000
of personality in which I

00:27:22.000 --> 00:27:24.180
was able to finally just

00:27:24.180 --> 00:27:25.759
take that leap of faith.

00:27:26.880 --> 00:27:27.859
I also think that

00:27:27.859 --> 00:27:29.059
my relationship with

00:27:29.079 --> 00:27:31.339
God in that time was

00:27:31.339 --> 00:27:32.920
important as well.

00:27:34.859 --> 00:27:35.940
Being able to listen

00:27:35.940 --> 00:27:37.880
to God audibly too

00:27:37.880 --> 00:27:39.359
was very important.

00:27:40.400 --> 00:27:41.259
My Catholic faith,

00:27:42.099 --> 00:27:43.140
having returned back

00:27:43.140 --> 00:27:44.180
to the sacraments

00:27:44.839 --> 00:27:45.599
obviously gave me

00:27:45.619 --> 00:27:46.319
a lot of strength,

00:27:46.720 --> 00:27:47.460
a lot of grace

00:27:47.460 --> 00:27:48.819
that I don't think I

00:27:48.819 --> 00:27:49.720
would have had otherwise.

00:27:50.859 --> 00:27:52.059
So I think it's

00:27:52.059 --> 00:27:55.839
going to depend on where

00:27:55.839 --> 00:27:57.019
everyone is at in

00:27:57.019 --> 00:27:57.940
their life in that moment.

00:27:58.099 --> 00:27:59.960
So in that regard,

00:28:00.200 --> 00:28:00.819
I always want to

00:28:00.819 --> 00:28:01.980
be very mindful

00:28:01.980 --> 00:28:04.140
that if someone is

00:28:04.220 --> 00:28:05.779
experiencing this,

00:28:06.779 --> 00:28:07.380
I don't want

00:28:07.380 --> 00:28:07.880
to tell them,

00:28:07.880 --> 00:28:08.400
oh, just quit your

00:28:08.400 --> 00:28:10.099
job because it's

00:28:10.099 --> 00:28:10.740
not that easy.

00:28:12.519 --> 00:28:13.440
Even my priest, when

00:28:13.440 --> 00:28:14.400
I went to confess

00:28:14.400 --> 00:28:16.099
and I told him

00:28:16.099 --> 00:28:17.000
where I was working,

00:28:17.619 --> 00:28:18.700
even my priest knew

00:28:18.700 --> 00:28:20.160
he couldn't just say,

00:28:20.259 --> 00:28:20.839
Ramona, you need to

00:28:20.839 --> 00:28:21.359
quit your job

00:28:21.680 --> 00:28:23.059
right now, tomorrow, whatever.

00:28:23.460 --> 00:28:24.180
He said, Ramona,

00:28:25.000 --> 00:28:25.640
this is going to be

00:28:25.640 --> 00:28:26.500
difficult for you,

00:28:26.799 --> 00:28:27.259
but you need to

00:28:27.259 --> 00:28:27.900
quit your job as

00:28:27.900 --> 00:28:28.539
soon as possible.

00:28:29.900 --> 00:28:30.500
And so I think

00:28:30.500 --> 00:28:32.119
for someone who is on

00:28:32.119 --> 00:28:33.160
the fence, who's worried,

00:28:33.640 --> 00:28:35.799
who's maybe experiencing

00:28:35.799 --> 00:28:37.599
this conviction going

00:28:37.599 --> 00:28:38.539
through this process,

00:28:39.079 --> 00:28:39.480
then I would

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:40.920
say turn to God.

00:28:41.640 --> 00:28:42.720
And if maybe they're

00:28:42.720 --> 00:28:43.740
not a person of faith,

00:28:44.880 --> 00:28:45.539
turn to someone

00:28:45.539 --> 00:28:46.160
they can trust,

00:28:46.940 --> 00:28:47.559
turn to someone

00:28:47.680 --> 00:28:48.380
who loves them.

00:28:49.279 --> 00:28:50.539
And that way they

00:28:50.539 --> 00:28:51.559
know that this person

00:28:51.559 --> 00:28:52.539
is going to be

00:28:52.539 --> 00:28:54.019
there and be their support.

00:28:55.339 --> 00:28:55.980
But I would definitely

00:28:55.980 --> 00:28:57.039
say turn to

00:28:57.039 --> 00:28:58.240
even the pro-lifers,

00:28:59.140 --> 00:29:00.119
because even if you

00:29:00.119 --> 00:29:00.900
don't believe in

00:29:00.900 --> 00:29:01.700
God or you don't

00:29:01.700 --> 00:29:02.319
have that religion,

00:29:03.200 --> 00:29:04.059
the pro-lifers are

00:29:04.059 --> 00:29:04.960
not going to reject you.

00:29:05.480 --> 00:29:06.119
They're still going to

00:29:06.119 --> 00:29:07.259
be there to support you

00:29:07.259 --> 00:29:08.839
and be your lifeline

00:29:08.839 --> 00:29:10.579
if you choose to leave.

00:29:11.380 --> 00:29:12.240
But yeah, I would

00:29:12.240 --> 00:29:14.519
definitely say turn to people

00:29:14.519 --> 00:29:16.140
who are willing to

00:29:16.140 --> 00:29:17.259
love you through the process,

00:29:17.259 --> 00:29:18.880
because it's not something

00:29:18.880 --> 00:29:20.519
that's very easy to do.

00:29:21.880 --> 00:29:22.460
And then, of course,

00:29:22.539 --> 00:29:23.099
if you are

00:29:23.099 --> 00:29:23.880
a person of faith,

00:29:24.519 --> 00:29:26.059
then turn to God.

00:29:26.420 --> 00:29:28.339
And if you've been living

00:29:28.339 --> 00:29:29.619
a life away from God,

00:29:30.299 --> 00:29:32.319
then start living your

00:29:32.319 --> 00:29:34.000
life toward God again,

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:36.960
because he definitely wants

00:29:36.960 --> 00:29:37.799
to receive us

00:29:37.799 --> 00:29:38.980
back into his arms.

00:29:40.700 --> 00:29:41.980
The other thing that's

00:29:41.980 --> 00:29:43.240
important is not

00:29:43.240 --> 00:29:44.720
to worry that God

00:29:44.720 --> 00:29:45.619
won't forgive you,

00:29:45.940 --> 00:29:46.779
because he will.

00:29:47.299 --> 00:29:48.119
There's nothing that we

00:29:48.119 --> 00:29:49.519
can do that

00:29:49.519 --> 00:29:50.880
God cannot forgive us

00:29:50.880 --> 00:29:51.779
for when we come

00:29:51.779 --> 00:29:53.319
with a contrite heart

00:29:53.799 --> 00:29:54.740
asking for his mercy.

00:29:58.200 --> 00:29:58.700
Thank you.

00:29:58.940 --> 00:30:00.920
Thank you again

00:30:01.500 --> 00:30:02.779
for sharing your story.

00:30:04.599 --> 00:30:05.099
And

00:30:05.380 --> 00:30:07.099
we are almost at

00:30:07.099 --> 00:30:08.700
the end of this episode,

00:30:08.859 --> 00:30:10.039
but now tell me,

00:30:10.880 --> 00:30:11.839
how has your life

00:30:12.140 --> 00:30:13.599
changed and what

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:14.299
are you doing now?

00:30:16.259 --> 00:30:17.900
Oh, my life has

00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:19.099
changed so much.

00:30:20.160 --> 00:30:20.880
I would say in many

00:30:20.880 --> 00:30:21.539
ways it's still

00:30:21.539 --> 00:30:22.619
similar, you know,

00:30:23.140 --> 00:30:25.099
but in the most important

00:30:25.099 --> 00:30:26.099
ways it's different

00:30:26.099 --> 00:30:28.640
in that everything that I

00:30:28.640 --> 00:30:30.539
do now is for God.

00:30:31.200 --> 00:30:32.740
I used to be someone

00:30:32.740 --> 00:30:33.599
who cared about

00:30:33.599 --> 00:30:34.319
what people thought,

00:30:35.380 --> 00:30:36.299
you know, a little

00:30:36.299 --> 00:30:37.299
bit of a people pleaser.

00:30:38.240 --> 00:30:39.099
I was afraid, you

00:30:39.099 --> 00:30:40.920
know, to rock the

00:30:40.920 --> 00:30:42.079
boat, so they say.

00:30:44.099 --> 00:30:45.319
And one of the

00:30:45.319 --> 00:30:46.460
things that God gave me

00:30:46.460 --> 00:30:46.900
through this

00:30:46.900 --> 00:30:49.230
conversion was courage.

00:30:50.039 --> 00:30:51.200
I found a courage

00:30:51.200 --> 00:30:52.359
in myself that I didn't

00:30:52.359 --> 00:30:53.259
know that I had,

00:30:53.759 --> 00:30:54.799
and I realized that

00:30:55.240 --> 00:30:56.180
I had to live

00:30:56.180 --> 00:30:58.000
my life with conviction.

00:30:58.640 --> 00:30:59.740
And part of that

00:30:59.740 --> 00:31:01.180
was not just conviction on

00:31:01.180 --> 00:31:02.099
this issue of life,

00:31:02.579 --> 00:31:03.579
but also conviction

00:31:03.579 --> 00:31:05.420
regarding my faith,

00:31:05.599 --> 00:31:06.180
my Catholic faith,

00:31:06.660 --> 00:31:07.960
because I realized how

00:31:07.960 --> 00:31:09.400
important that was to me.

00:31:10.299 --> 00:31:13.000
And so now I live

00:31:13.000 --> 00:31:15.859
my life solely caring

00:31:15.859 --> 00:31:16.680
about what God

00:31:16.680 --> 00:31:17.799
thinks and not

00:31:17.799 --> 00:31:18.599
caring about what

00:31:18.599 --> 00:31:19.740
anybody else thinks.

00:31:20.519 --> 00:31:21.819
And then also,

00:31:22.519 --> 00:31:23.940
obviously,

00:31:24.420 --> 00:31:26.559
it changed by being because

00:31:26.559 --> 00:31:28.000
we were open to life,

00:31:28.000 --> 00:31:29.019
we were able to

00:31:29.059 --> 00:31:29.740
have more children

00:31:29.740 --> 00:31:30.680
because of that.

00:31:30.859 --> 00:31:32.099
We have children who

00:31:32.099 --> 00:31:32.960
are alive today

00:31:32.960 --> 00:31:34.279
that wouldn't be here

00:31:34.279 --> 00:31:35.799
otherwise because we

00:31:35.799 --> 00:31:36.500
were never going to

00:31:36.500 --> 00:31:37.160
have more children.

00:31:37.799 --> 00:31:38.460
So I look at

00:31:38.859 --> 00:31:40.119
their faces and I think,

00:31:40.500 --> 00:31:41.220
you know, wow,

00:31:41.740 --> 00:31:43.779
they're here today

00:31:43.779 --> 00:31:45.150
because of my conversion.

00:31:45.250 --> 00:31:47.960
And I think about the

00:31:47.960 --> 00:31:48.980
people who were involved

00:31:48.980 --> 00:31:50.059
in 40 Days for Life.

00:31:50.400 --> 00:31:51.380
And when we go

00:31:51.380 --> 00:31:51.880
out on the

00:31:51.880 --> 00:31:53.039
sidewalk and we pray,

00:31:53.819 --> 00:31:54.680
we often think

00:31:54.680 --> 00:31:56.460
about saving babies

00:31:56.460 --> 00:31:57.160
and saving lives.

00:31:58.339 --> 00:31:59.099
And I don't know

00:31:59.099 --> 00:32:00.299
that anyone has ever really

00:32:00.299 --> 00:32:01.859
considered they did

00:32:01.859 --> 00:32:03.099
save lives with me.

00:32:03.200 --> 00:32:03.819
Not only did they

00:32:03.819 --> 00:32:04.839
save my soul,

00:32:05.380 --> 00:32:06.000
but look at the

00:32:06.019 --> 00:32:06.640
children that are

00:32:06.640 --> 00:32:08.019
alive today as a

00:32:08.019 --> 00:32:09.079
result, my children.

00:32:09.839 --> 00:32:11.180
And so they're here.

00:32:11.500 --> 00:32:12.440
Their lives are saved.

00:32:12.960 --> 00:32:13.940
They're alive today

00:32:14.160 --> 00:32:15.200
because I left the

00:32:15.200 --> 00:32:16.039
abortion industry.

00:32:16.519 --> 00:32:17.440
So that's another

00:32:17.440 --> 00:32:18.420
beautiful way in

00:32:18.420 --> 00:32:19.160
which it's changed.

00:32:19.839 --> 00:32:21.440
But another is just the

00:32:21.440 --> 00:32:22.240
way that I look at

00:32:22.259 --> 00:32:23.279
life as a woman

00:32:23.279 --> 00:32:24.380
and as a wife

00:32:24.380 --> 00:32:25.140
and as a mother.

00:32:25.279 --> 00:32:25.700
And I'm also

00:32:25.700 --> 00:32:26.279
a grandmother.

00:32:27.039 --> 00:32:28.359
Yes. Yes. Thank you.

00:32:28.660 --> 00:32:32.299
And so recognizing that that

00:32:32.299 --> 00:32:33.579
my role as a wife

00:32:33.579 --> 00:32:34.339
and a mother and

00:32:34.339 --> 00:32:36.039
grandmother is number one,

00:32:36.640 --> 00:32:37.259
that there's

00:32:37.279 --> 00:32:38.140
nothing else that's

00:32:38.140 --> 00:32:38.619
going to be more

00:32:38.619 --> 00:32:40.240
important than that.

00:32:41.980 --> 00:32:44.380
Really embracing the

00:32:44.380 --> 00:32:45.980
vocation of motherhood,

00:32:46.619 --> 00:32:48.119
where before I hadn't

00:32:48.119 --> 00:32:49.140
really considered it.

00:32:49.259 --> 00:32:49.839
Never give it

00:32:49.839 --> 00:32:50.359
any thought.

00:32:50.799 --> 00:32:51.380
And I always thought

00:32:51.380 --> 00:32:52.420
that my worth and my

00:32:52.420 --> 00:32:54.319
value was based off

00:32:54.319 --> 00:32:55.480
of what I could contribute

00:32:55.720 --> 00:32:56.680
and in other ways,

00:32:56.720 --> 00:32:57.359
like outside

00:32:57.359 --> 00:32:57.900
of the home,

00:32:58.400 --> 00:33:00.339
rather than really recognizing

